// xcode project - start with empty project
//
// 1. on the general project add "settings.xcconfig" configuration for debug and release
//
// 2. Drag frameworks to project - remember to COPY
//
//    Qt:
//    open  $QTDIR/lib
//    QtCore QtXml QtGui QtWidgets
//
// 3. add library target "gsplash"
//    a. remove gsplash and other files created
//    b. source is gsplash (build phases)
//    c. add the qt frameworks to target if its not set already
//
// 4. add command tools example, source is example.cc
//    remove main.cpp created
//    add libraries and frameworks accordingly:
//    a. add libraries gsplash in build phases "dependencies" and libraries
